 Install Jenkins -> yum install jenkins -y
                                            ->  sudo wget -O /etc/yum.repos.d/jenkins.repo https://pkg.jenkins.io/redhat/jenkins.repo
                                             -> sudo rpm --import https://pkg.jenkins.io/redhat/jenkins.io.key

 install maven ->yum install maven -y
      steps to create maven project :
            -> mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=com.mycompany.app -DartifactId=my-app -DarchetypeArtifactId=maven-archetype-quickstart
                                                    -DarchetypeVersion=1.4 -DinteractiveMode=false
           -> cd my-app
          
           -> mvn package (this will build the project)
